name: Eternal Bride
description:
From collection : "lost times"

She is standing there
  Always in white
Her smile is the sea
And her look is the warm summer sun
  The wind is a net, falls on her face
And the green of the forest in her heart
She is standing there
young forever
always happy
always beautiful
And she does not want to put her foot out of this frame
To the real world
To the world of pain
To the world of sorrow
She stands there forever
forever
Always
Beautiful, happy, young, colorful 
She is immortalized in the image
The Eternal Bride of Time
